<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Students in the Spanish minor gain basic proficiency in Spanish and learn the language, literature, and traditions of the Spanish-speaking world. In today’s global economy, this minor is an asset to almost any major.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
